{
    "esm": "0.4.0",
    "metadata": {
        "name": "DryDepositionGas",
        "description": "Wesley (1989) gas-phase dry deposition model. Computes dry deposition velocities v_* [m/s] and rates k_* [1/s] for 132 atmospheric trace gas species. Each species is characterized by its GasData (Dh2oPerDx, Hstar, Fo) constants from Wesely (1989) Table 2 and extended GEOS-Chem species data. The deposition velocity v_i = ifelse(lev==1,1,0) / (Ra + Rb_i + Rc_i) where Ra is the aerodynamic resistance (shared), Rb_i = 5*Sc_i^(2/3)/u_star is the quasi-laminar sublayer resistance, and Rc_i is the Wesley (1989) surface resistance computed inline with species constants substituted. Rain and dew are hardcoded false in the upstream DryDepositionGas builder. Migrated from AtmosphericDeposition.jl@e4468c79 src/dry_deposition.jl:323.",
        "tags": [
            "atmospheric_deposition",
            "dry-deposition",
            "wesley-1989",
            "multi-species",
            "gas-phase"
        ],
        "created": "2026-05-30T00:00:00Z",
        "authors": [
            "AtmosphericDeposition.jl contributors",
            "EarthSciModels migration (esm-qtoc)"
        ],
        "references": [
            {
                "citation": "Wesely, M. L. (1989). Parameterization of surface resistances to gaseous dry deposition in regional-scale numerical models. Atmospheric Environment 23(6), 1293-1304. doi:10.1016/0004-6981(89)90153-4"
            },
            {
                "citation": "Seinfeld, J. H., & Pandis, S. N. (2006). Atmospheric Chemistry and Physics: From Air Pollution to Climate Change (2nd ed.). Wiley. Eqs. 19.13-19.14 (aerodynamic resistance), 19.17 (quasi-laminar resistance for gases)."
            },
            {
                "citation": "Source: AtmosphericDeposition.jl/src/dry_deposition.jl (commit e4468c79c8dd4aae88646cd16d6bcf290874742c). `DryDepositionGas` builder function (line 323)."
            }
        ]
    },
    "models": {
        "DryDepositionGas": {
            "reference": {
                "citation": "Wesely, M. L. (1989). Parameterization of surface resistances to gaseous dry deposition in regional-scale numerical models. Atmospheric Environment 23(6), 1293-1304. doi:10.1016/0004-6981(89)90153-4",
                "notes": "source_ref: AtmosphericDeposition.jl@e4468c79c8dd4aae88646cd16d6bcf290874742c:src/dry_deposition.jl:323\n\nUpstream `DryDepositionGas` is an MTK builder that declares 12 scalar @parameters (season, landuse, z, del_P, z_0, u_star, L, rho_A, G, Ts, theta, lev) and builds equations depvel .~ DryDepGas.(...) and deprate .~ depvel .* g .* rho_A ./ del_P for 132 gas species. The species GasData (Dh2oPerDx, Hstar, Fo) are constants from src/wesley1989.jl. rain=false and dew=false are hardcoded in the builder.\n\nFor each species i, DryDepGas computes:\n  v_i = ifelse(lev==1,1,0) / (Ra + Rb_i + Rc_i)\n  Ra = ra(z, z0, u_star, L) [aerodynamic resistance, shared]\n  Rb_i = 5 * Sc_i^(2/3) / u_star [quasi-laminar, Seinfeld & Pandis Eq. 19.17]\n  Sc_i = mu(Ts) / (rho_A * dH2O(Ts) / Dh2oPerDx_i) [Schmidt number]\n  Rc_i = WesleySurfaceResistance(GasData_i, G, Ts-273, theta, season, landuse, false, false, isSO2_i, isO3_i)\n\nMigration approach: Ra, mu_air, Dh2o, and the 7 Wesley table lookups plus rs, rdc, correction are computed as shared observed variables. For each species, species-specific parts (Rb, Rc) are inlined into the v_* expression with GasData constants substituted. Since rain=false and dew=false, rlux=rlux_dry for all species and the rs rain/dew multiplier=1.\n\nSO2 (species 131): isSO2=true \u2192 rclx=r_clS_val, rgsx=r_gsS_val.\nO3 (species 114): isO3=true \u2192 rclx=r_clO_val, rgsx=r_gsO_val.\nAll other species: rclx=1/(Hstar/(1e5*r_clS)+Fo/r_clO), rgsx=1/(Hstar/(1e5*r_gsS)+Fo/r_gsO).\n\nTemperature convention: Ts parameter is in Kelvin (default 298K). mu_air and Dh2o use Ts directly (Kelvin). Wesley surface resistance uses Ts_c = Ts - 273 (Celsius), consistent with the upstream (Ts * T_unitless - 273) conversion in DryDepGas.\n\nNeutral-stability: L=0 is the neutral-stability sentinel. zeta and zeta_0 are reformulated as z*L/(L^2+1e-300) and z0*L/(L^2+1e-300) to avoid division by zero, per dry_aerosol.esm convention.\n\nTolerance (model-level rel=1e-6): closed-form algebraic system; interp.linear table lookups land on integer knots (zero blend weight), subsequent arithmetic accumulates ~1e-13 float64 round-off. rel=1e-6 provides comfortable headroom."
            },
            "tolerance": {
                "rel": 1e-06
            },
            "variables": {
                "season": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 1,
                    "description": "Wesley (1989) season index (1=midsummer, 2=autumn, 3=late autumn, 4=winter, 5=transitional). Upstream parameter `season`, default wesleyMidsummer=1."
                },
                "landuse": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 1,
                    "description": "Wesley (1989) land-use index (1=urban, 2=agricultural, 3=range, 4=deciduous, 5=coniferous, 6=mixed forest, 7=water, 8=barren, 9=wetland, 10=range/ag, 11=rocky shrubs). Upstream parameter `landuse`, default wesleyUrban=1."
                },
                "z": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 60.0,
                    "description": "Height from ground to mid-point of level 1 [m]."
                },
                "del_P": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "Pa",
                    "default": 1520.0,
                    "description": "Pressure thickness of atmospheric level 1 [Pa]."
                },
                "z0": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 0.04,
                    "description": "Surface roughness length [m]. Upstream z_0."
                },
                "u_star": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m/s",
                    "default": 0.44,
                    "description": "Friction velocity [m/s]."
                },
                "L": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 0.0,
                    "description": "Monin-Obukhov length [m]. L=0 is the neutral-stability sentinel."
                },
                "rho_A": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "kg/m^3",
                    "default": 1.2,
                    "description": "Air density [kg/m^3]. Upstream rho_A."
                },
                "G": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "W/m^2",
                    "default": 300.0,
                    "description": "Solar irradiation [W/m^2]."
                },
                "Ts": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "K",
                    "default": 298.0,
                    "description": "Surface air temperature [K]. Converted to Celsius (Ts_c = Ts - 273) for Wesley surface resistance."
                },
                "theta": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 0.0,
                    "description": "Slope of the local terrain [radians]. Upstream theta."
                },
                "lev": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 1,
                    "description": "Atmospheric level index. Deposition is active only when lev==1."
                },
                "g_const": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m/s^2",
                    "default": 9.81,
                    "description": "Gravitational acceleration [m/s^2]. Upstream @constants g."
                },
                "kappa": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 0.4,
                    "description": "Von Karman constant. Upstream @constants kappa."
                },
                "Ts_c": {
                    "type": "observed",
                    "units": "1",
                    "description": "Surface temperature in Celsius, Ts_c = Ts - 273. Passed to WesleySurfaceResistance (which uses Celsius).",
                    "expression": {
                        "op": "-",
                        "args": [
                            "Ts",
                            273.0
                        ]
                    }
                },
                "L2_eps": {
                    "type": "observed",
                    "units": "m^2",
                    "description": "L^2 + 1e-300 denominator used to regularize division by L at neutral stability.",
                    "expression": {
                        "op": "+",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "*",
                                "args": [
                                    "L",
                                    "L"
                                ]
                            },
                            1e-300
                        ]
                    }
                },
                "zeta": {
                    "type": "observed",
                    "units": "1",
                    "description": "Monin-Obukhov stability parameter z/L (regularized to avoid division by zero at L=0).",
                    "expression": {
                        "op": "/",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "*",
                                "args": [
                                    "z",
                                    "L"
                                ]
                            },
                            "L2_eps"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                "zeta_0": {
                    "type": "observed",
                    "units": "1",
                    "description": "Monin-Obukhov stability parameter z0/L (regularized).",
                    "expression": {
                        "op": "/",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "*",
                                "args": [
                                    "z0",
                                    "L"
                                ]
                            },
                            "L2_eps"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                "ra_neutral_stable": {
                    "type": "observed",
                    "units": "s/m",
                    "description": "Aerodynamic resistance for neutral/stable conditions (zeta >= 0). Stable: adds 4.7*(zeta-zeta_0) term.",
                    "expression": {
                        "op": "ifelse",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "<",
                                "args": [
                                    0,
                                    "zeta"
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "op": "*",
                                "args": [
                                    {
                                        "op": "/",
                                        "args": [
                                            1,
                                            {
                                                "op": "*",
                                                "args": [
                                                    "kappa",
                                                    "u_star"
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "op": "+",
                                        "args": [
                                            {
                                                "op": "log",
                                                "args": [
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "/",
                                                        "args": [
                                                            "z",
                                                            "z0"
                                                        ]
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "op": "*",
                                                "args": [
                                                    4.7,
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "-",
                                                        "args": [
                                                            "zeta",
                                                            "zeta_0"
                                                        ]
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "op": "*",
                                "args": [
                                    {
                                        "op": "/",
                                        "args": [
                                            1,
                                            {
                                                "op": "*",
                                                "args": [
                                                    "kappa",
                                                    "u_star"
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "op": "log",
                                        "args": [
                                            {
                                                "op": "/",
                                                "args": [
                                                    "z",
                                                    "z0"
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                "i_unstable": {
                    "type": "observed",
                    "units": "1",
                    "description": "Guard flag: 1 when zeta<0 (unstable), 0 otherwise. Prevents domain error in eta calculation.",
                    "expression": {
                        "op": "ifelse",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "<",
                                "args": [
                                    "zeta",
                                    0
                                ]
                            },
                            1,
                            0
                        ]
                    }
                },
                "eta_0": {
                    "type": "observed",
                    "units": "1",
                    "description": "Stability correction factor eta_0 = (1 - 15*zeta_0*i_unstable)^(1/4) for unstable regime.",
                    "expression": {
                        "op": "^",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "-",
                                "args": [
                                    1,
                                    {
                                        "op": "*",
                                        "args": [
