                    "type": "observed",
                    "units": "s/m",
                    "description": "Aerodynamic resistance Ra [s/m] (Seinfeld & Pandis 2006 Eq. 19.13-19.14). Three stability regimes: unstable (zeta<0), neutral (zeta=0), stable (zeta>0).",
